            <title><![CDATA[澳大利亚就中国招募澳前飞行员报道展开调查]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>澳大利亚正在调查有关中国军方试图招募前澳洲防军飞行员提供训练服务的报道，并且发现“足够的证据”，认为此问题值得深入调查。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>据彭博社报道，澳洲</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>国防部长</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>马勒斯</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>星期三（11月9日）在堪培拉告诉记者，国防部初步调查发现了“足够的证据”，值得对这个问题进行深入调查。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>马勒斯指出，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>任何前军人透露政府的秘密信息，都是显而易见、明白无误的犯罪。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
